name: Availdom
tagline: node.js wrapper for checking availablity of domain name
body:
### Welcome to availdom
This is a node.js Wrapper for checking the availability of a domain name by just installing this package using npm and make a call to the desired function() . 


### Authors and Contributors
Ritish Gumber (@ritishgumber) , 2016
___
### Installation 
[npm package](https://www.npmjs.com/package/availdom)
___
### Support or Contact
Raise [Issues](https://github.com/ritishgumber/availdom/issues) here.
